{
  "title": "Welcome to Our Brand New Newsletter, ‘The Daily List!’",
  "author": "R&I Editorial Team",
  "date_published": "2018-10-01",
  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"contents\">\n<div class=\"avtempclass\" id=\"post-thumbnail\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-post-image\" decoding=\"async\" fetchpriority=\"high\" height=\"525\" sizes=\"(max-width: 700px) 100vw, 700px\" src=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CheckUsOut-10_01_18-V10-700x525.jpg\" srcset=\"https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CheckUsOut-10_01_18-V10.jpg 700w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CheckUsOut-10_01_18-V10-250x188.jpg 250w, https://riskandinsurance.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/CheckUsOut-10_01_18-V10-120x90.jpg 120w\" width=\"700\"/> </div>\n<p>Starting this week, our new email format will highlight 5 original stories along with the current trending stories on the <em>Risk &amp; Insurance® </em>website. This new newsletter simplifies and consolidates the multiple newsletters we used to send on a weekly basis. You can expect to receive “The Daily List” on most work days — we skip the days you have better things to do, like holidays and summer Fridays.</p>\n<p>This new email is part of a broader revamp of our entire digital publishing platform. If you haven’t visited us in a while, <a href=\"http://click1.email.riskandinsurance.com/skrrskwwvvmtbvzjtcggftzkjgtlfgzzlldkpmcvlrsc_lhjjjzgk.html\">check out our new homepage</a>, updated with relevant and interesting content each day.</p><div class=\"ad-small show-mobile\">\n<div id=\"div-gpt-ad-1632840501295-7\">\n\n</div></div>\n<p>Also be sure to follow us on <a href=\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/risk-insurance/\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">LinkedIn</a>, <a href=\"https://twitter.com/RiskInsurance\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Twitter</a> and <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/RiskInsuranceMag/?modal=admin_todo_tour\" rel=\"noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Facebook</a>. And, as always, we highly value your continued support and welcome any feedback you might want to share. Feel free to reach us at <a class=\"__cf_email__\" data-cfemail=\"2d5f445e4641485959485f5e6d415f5d034e4240\" href=\"/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection\">[email protected]</a>.</p>\n<div class=\"bio\">The R&amp;I Editorial Team can be reached at <a class=\"__cf_email__\" data-cfemail=\"39545c5d50585a56574d585a4d794d515c50574a4d504d4c4d5c4a17564b5e\" href=\"/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection\">[email protected]</a>.</div>\n<div class=\"pad-1\"> </div>\n<div class=\"actions\">\n</div>\n</div></body></html>",
